# @sfcr/chat-api

- Cloudflare Worker for OpenAI proxy / notebook assistant and draft-eval API; `noEmit` TypeScript.
- Local secrets: `.dev.vars` (gitignored); never commit API keys.
- Browser connects via `VITE_NOTEBOOK_ASSISTANT_API_URL`; frontend must not embed secrets.
- Tests: `packages/chat-api/test/`. Deploy/docs: `packages/chat-api/README.md`.
